      "agenda": "Protect Iskra and devour as many humans as possible.",
      "gifts": [
        "Big Wolf: Greskar is an enormous black wolf, as big as a horse. When he grabs someone with his jaws, in addition to inflicting a Wound, he can drag or hurl them away as if they were a rag doll. Once per Scene, Greskar's bite can inflict 1 additional Wound.",
        "The Wolf's Smell: Greskar's sense of smell is infallible. The big wolf will always be able to identify someone if he knows their scent, ignoring all kinds of disguises and even magic."
